Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.65,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:22.16,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My brain trembles...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:23.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Puck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.63,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:35.00,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Complacency! Negligence! That is sloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:38.26,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You should have killed me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.94,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the power you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you failed to do what you needed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.56,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:50.02,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly want to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.91,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Then grow a thousand shadows,\Nhalf of what Satella could...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... Puck?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:10.30,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.30,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's cruel of me to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.57,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.60,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,This is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:21.95,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,A mere spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:23.31,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I've devoted my love to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:26.87,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,At the hands of a mere spirit—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:31.19,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,A human who's only lived a few decades \Nshouldn't talk to a spirit about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:35.07,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Time has nothing to do with \Nthe depth of one's faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.13,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you wouldn't liken me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:41.03,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,to a fool like you, a being\Nthat lives for eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.63,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,but wastes most of it in idleness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:49.04,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ah, my brain is tremblinglinglingling...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:49.04,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Death isn't even a punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.63,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.07,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The Ordeal has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:57.30,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my body dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my wishes will be called to \Nthe exalted witch's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll receive her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.56,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to our reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:07.47,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,He quit while he was ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.71,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we have a little talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:17.10,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, you have committed three sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.91,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,First, you broke your promise to Lia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.54,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to understand \Nhow important a promise is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.69,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,to a spirit-arts user.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.75,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Second, you ignored Lia's \Nwishes and returned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.42,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,And third...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.31,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You let Lia die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:42.92,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with my contract,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.33,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I will now destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:47.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:48.52,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Lia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:53.33,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia is my entire reason for existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.48,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason for me to \Nexist in a world without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.83,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,The fog is coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.74,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a troublesome \None has been drawn here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.16,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:08.40,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I suppose they call\Nit the White Whale now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.80,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You called it here, let Lia die,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.78,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,and now, you die yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.26,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You really are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.57,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard this laugh before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.33,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The voice of a man I hated to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.67,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:30.89,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm laughing at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:34.46,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I let Rem die, killed Emilia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.90,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and now, I'm going to die in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.62,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I really am so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.36,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are slothful, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.20,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.41,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:53.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm your Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.73,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.97,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,This crowd is tiring you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:04.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of energy, worn down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.50,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was feeling kind of stressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,so I skipped out on explaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.23,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you mustn't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:49.83,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that you are giving a great \Ndeal of thought to our situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.98,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't dislike it when\Nyou are so forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:05:01.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you've seen me just being pathetic, \Ndepressed all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:06.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've bothered a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with all my contemplating and agonizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:14.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I finally figured out how \Nto take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Or, when I really think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was told what to do from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:22.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know when to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.28,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But I think that is what's so \Nwonderful about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Things I've realized\Nand been forced to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:35.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds of experiences have brought me here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I've actually had the \Nanswer for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.03,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Run away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to leave the\Ncapital, to head far west.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe north.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I heard no one can enter the southern kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so one of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like cold weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd personally recommend west.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.52,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, it could be a long journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I know this is a snap decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,so it won't be easy—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The way you said that makes it sound as if
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:23.58,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,you plan to go to some other \Ncountry that isn't Lugunica...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.02,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:29.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, it must be because \Nyou've had another great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.65,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will help Emilia-sama \Nand Roswaal-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what this is, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:38.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:42.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd be just as powerless if \NI went back to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So run away with me, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:52.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what everyone has been telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've denied it with all my might, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:04.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:09.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's been spelled out for me, over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:14.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I do will just lead to a dead body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe more, depending on what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't be in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.75,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But this is so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:36.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it's sudden, I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:43.69,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Or someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:47.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a dragon-drawn \Ncarriage and head west.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:56.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave Lugunica and go far \Nwest... To Kararagi, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll buy a little house\Nand live there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if bad things happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can keep going if you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just having someone waiting at \Nhome for me with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how tired I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I know you're waiting for me, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please choose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you choose me, I'll\Ngive you all that I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Live with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:37.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot run away with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.95,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to laugh together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as we talk about the future, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:48.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can't laugh now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, once we actually get moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we can—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I have thought about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.86,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We would arrive in Kararagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rent a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we had a home and work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we would get by somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:10.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, thanks to Roswaal-sama, \NI have received an education,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:14.71,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,so I think I could easily find \Nwork, even in Kararagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:18.14,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You might have to either\Nlook for manual labor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:22.33,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,or take care of things around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.74,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Once we had a stable income,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we could look for a better place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, you could study
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for perhaps a year, so that you can find
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:36.68,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,a decent job, until you can actually work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.04,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We would work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once we had enough money, \Nperhaps we could buy a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.58,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we could even open a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.28,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Kararagi is a\Nthriving commercial area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:53.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we could earn a living \Non one of your fanciful ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.82,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And once our jobs were on track...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's embarrassing to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we could have a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.61,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It would be half-demon and half-human,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm certain it would be feisty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.08,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we have a boy or a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,twins or even triplets,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they would be adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it wouldn't be all fun times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:17.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And not everything would \Nwork out as I imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.08,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We might have only daughters and no sons,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:25.85,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,so you might not feel very\Nproud of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:26.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.77,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But... But... Even when the children grow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.97,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and reach the age where they \Nstart to treat you coldly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.39,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I shall still be on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:38.53,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We will be famous in the neighborhood \Nas a couple of old lovebirds,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:43.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,as we take our time spending life \Ntogether and growing old...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:44.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.75,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I would feel bad for doing it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.65,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,but I would prefer to die\Nbefore you, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.95,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die quietly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lying on our bed, with your hand in mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.31,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded by our children and their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:11:01.07,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,To say, "I was so happy,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you all look on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:10.11,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I could end my life happily, so happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:15.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it that badly, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:20.14,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If you could wish for that\Nfuture with a smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:24.45,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I would be truly happy to die that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.30,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I could live with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:34.20,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Just knowing that you want me \Nwith you when you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.76,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,makes me happy, from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.51,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that if we run away together now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:48.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I would be leaving behind the \NSubaru-kun that I love most.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:50.67,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:57.11,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot, please trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I shall do something to make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, at least, we should go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.32,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If we take our time,\Nand consider things calmly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we will find a different answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've already agonized over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:18.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.80,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to give up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing easy about giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm just doing nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking about nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,cutting myself off from everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and throwing everything away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:44.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And that's all it took to give up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was not easy to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:52.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much easier for me to think
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was something I could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The only path everything\Nleads to is giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I could do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:07.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I would... I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.59,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It is easy to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:18.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:22.77,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know what painful things \Nyou've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:27.26,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,or what you have done to make you suffer so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.30,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And I know it would be wrong of me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to thoughtlessly say I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.72,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But... But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.83,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,There is something that I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:45.05,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you're someone who cannot \Ngive up on something halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:50.51,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you are someone who can smile
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:54.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,when you talk about your\Nwishes for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.23,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:01.02,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you are someone who \Ncannot give up on the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that kind of—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I am not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.82,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't given up on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.05,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Not Emilia-sama or Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Roswaal-sama, or Beatrice-sama, \Nor anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have... I have given up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Carrying it all was impossible from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are so small,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it all slipped through\Nmy fingers, leaving nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.37,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't true. You have—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:34.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of man I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no strength, but I want it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no knowledge, but all I do is dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do,\Nbut I struggle in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All I do is talk a big game,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and make myself sound like a big shot, \Nwhen I can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I never do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet I can complain like a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Who do I think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:10.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that I can live like \Nthis and not feel ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:16.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Before I came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:26.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Before I got into the situation \Nthat led me to all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,do you have any idea what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I did nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:34.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done a single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:38.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I had all that time, all that freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I could have done anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I never did a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the result! What I \Nam now is the result!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All of my powerlessness,\Nall of my incompetence,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,is the product of my rotten character.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:56.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to accomplish something, \Nwhen I've never done anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,goes beyond the limits of arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The cost of my laziness and all \Nthe wasteful habits in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,just ends up killing both you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I thought I could go on \Nliving here, nothing changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:19.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That old man saw that part of me perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to get stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,or trying to make things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:29.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was just striking an obvious \Npose, to justify myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:35.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,to say that I was trying, that it wasn't \Nlike I wasn't doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to say I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be told that\Nit couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:45.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I only pretended to push my body to the \Nlimit, so that would be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I had you help me study,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:52.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was just posing to cover up \Nhow embarrassed I felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,At heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a small, cowardly,\Nfilthy piece of trash,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:01.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,who's always worried about how \Nothers see me. And nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing about me has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:12.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:15.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That all of it was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the lowest of the low.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:21.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely hate myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:31.18,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That no matter how deeply you \Nhave fallen into darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,you still have the courage \Nto reach out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love it when you stroke my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.91,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as if we can understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the contact between \Nyour hand and my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.98,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.50,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Just hearing you say one word
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,makes my heart feel warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.18,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.12,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, they look stern,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:59.14,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,but when you're being kind to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.10,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way they soften.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.63,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.98,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,For a boy, you have such lovely fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:12.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But when they clutch mine, \NI know they are the strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,slender fingers of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.68,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way you walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.81,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When we walk together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:25.77,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way you occasionally turn, \Nto make sure I keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.30,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way you look when you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.32,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You look unguarded, like an infant,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.59,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and your eyelashes are on the long side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.63,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When I touch your cheek, you calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:39.68,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And when I playfully touch your \Nlips, you don't even notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.85,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And it makes my heart ache terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:50.32,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When you said that you hate yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:53.04,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,it made me want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the wonderful things I know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That was all phony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know myself better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,All you know is yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:12.83,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know about \Nthe Subaru-kun that I see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:17.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why... do you like me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weak and small.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I ran away last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:28.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:32.72,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are my hero, Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.08,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,In that dark forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I didn't even know who I was anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.57,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and couldn't think of anything \Nbut violently lashing out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.78,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.62,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up unable to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and Sister was exhausted after \Nusing too much magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:53.92,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,you faced the mabeasts as a diversion, \Nso we could escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.17,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way you could win,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your life was in real danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.57,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But you still stayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:03.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and came back to my arms, still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When you woke up, you smiled,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:08.40,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and said the words I wanted to hear most,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.30,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,when I wanted to hear them most,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the one I wanted most to hear them from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:17.02,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My time has been stopped for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that fiery night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:23.03,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,the night I lost everything except my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:26.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,my time has been stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:30.94,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who melted my frozen heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:35.50,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and kindly made my stopped \Ntime begin to move forward again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:41.13,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have no idea how you saved me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:46.05,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,or how happy I was at that \Nmoment, on that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.80,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:52.94,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what painful things happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.74,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,even when it looks like you'll lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:59.02,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When no one else in the world believes in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.32,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,when you don't even believe in yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.82,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I will believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That the Subaru-kun who saved me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,is a true hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:33.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:37.07,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:41.07,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The Rem you saved is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:44.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done anything. I'm empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No one will even listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.38,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:52.39,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I will listen to anything you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.33,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No one expects anything of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No one believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:03.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:10.43,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I love you, Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:16.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't mind that it's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:19.35,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I want it to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:22.99,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I would not want for it to be anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:27.53,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot forgive yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for being empty and having nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:32.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,then let us start from here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Start what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:38.97,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you started my time for me \Nwhen it was stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:42.17,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,we will make the time that \Nyou feel is stopped for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,begin to move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:46.53,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Let us start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.31,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,From square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:51.52,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:53.73,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,from zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.62,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If it is too hard for you to walk alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will hold you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:05.78,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,As we walk, we will share the burden \Nand support each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:09.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this what you said to me that morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:14.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Show me how awesome you can be, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:17.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:19.41,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I love Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:28.27,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Emilia smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be of help to Emilia's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:35.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she says I'm in the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if she tells me to stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:45.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Using my feelings for her as an excuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:49.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,to get her to understand everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:51.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,was arrogant of me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if she doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:24:00.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a bleak,\Npainful future waiting for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:03.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take her away to a future \Nwhere we can all laugh together!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:09.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:12.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lack in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:17.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident that I can \Neven keep walking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.47,0:24:20.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weak, fragile, and small.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:24.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, to make sure I keep walking straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:26.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,to help me realize when I'm wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:27.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:33.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You are a cruel man, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:37.20,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You ask all this of someone you just rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:41.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's also hard for me to ask \Nthis of the one who rejected
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.37,0:24:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my once-in-a-lifetime proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.88,0:24:56.93,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.59,0:24:59.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If it will help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.41,0:25:02.04,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,my hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.49,0:25:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,greet the future with a smile, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.38,0:25:07.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.91,0:25:10.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You get a front row seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.58,0:25:17.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,To see the man you fell for
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.64,0:25:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,become the most awesome hero ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:33.71,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,552)}I'm watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.60,0:25:35.97,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.22,0:25:39.25,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't look downward.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.25,0:25:44.93,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru's story will begin \Nright here, from zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.00,0:25:51.83,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My life in another world\Nstarts here, from zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.90,0:25:55.90,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,From Ze{\c&HFBD8AD&}ro
